title: Mike Parson
added: In January 2021, Parson called up the [[Missouri National Guard]] to assist with the vaccination efforts, though he did say that "Supply [of the vaccine] remains extremely limited."<ref>{{cite web|title=Parson activates Missouri National Guard to help with administering COVID-19 vaccines|url=https://fox2now.com/video/parson-activates-missouri-national-guard-to-help-with-administering-covid-19-vaccines/6214002/|publisher=Fox 2|access-date=October 16, 2021}}</ref>
